Hi Chelsea! today I will teach you how to bake a cake. First, we need several eggs, a cup of milk, and of course the cake mix. Break the eggs in the bowl and add the milk and cake mix. After about 60 Strokes put the mixture into the oven and bake 30 minutes at 350 degree. Then you can have a delicious cake!